   Hengl, T (Corresponding Author), OpenGeoHub Fdn, Wageningen, Netherlands.
   Hengl, Tomislav; Wheeler, Ichsani, EnvirometriX Ltd, Wageningen, Netherlands.
   Hengl, Tomislav; Parente, Leandro; Sheykhmousa, Mohammadreza; MacMillan, Robert A.; Wheeler, Ichsani, OpenGeoHub Fdn, Wageningen, Netherlands.
