   Amini, Heresh, Univ Copenhagen, Fac Hlth \& Med Sci, Dept Publ Hlth, DK-1165 Copenhagen, Denmark.
   Shi, Liuhua, Emory Univ, Rollins Sch Publ Hlth, Gangarosa Dept Environm Hlth, Atlanta, GA 30322 USA.
   Requia, Weeberb J., Fundacao Getulio Vargas, Sch Publ Policy \& Govt, BR-72125590 Sao Paulo, SP, Brazil.},
DOI = {10.1021/acs.est.0c01791},
Keywords-Plus = {CANADIAN CENSUS HEALTH; LAND-USE REGRESSION; AIR-QUALITY;
   NITROGEN-DIOXIDE; AMBIENT PM2.5; SURFACE OZONE; URBAN AREAS; EXPOSURE;
   MODEL; MORTALITY},
