   Rossier, Nicolas, Agr Inst Fribourg Canton, Route Grangeneuve 31, CH-1725 Posieux, Switzerland.
   Schneider, Andre, INRA, UMR ISPA 1391, CS 20032, F-33882 Villenave Dornon, France.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.geoderma.2016.12.002},
Keywords = {Soil potassium; Soil properties; Terrain attributes; Land use; Spatial
   statistics; Autocorrelation; Random forest},
