Affiliation = {Chatterjee, S (Corresponding Author), Univ Calcutta, Dept Comp Sci \& Engn, Kolkata, India.
   Chatterjee, Sankhadeep, Univ Calcutta, Dept Comp Sci \& Engn, Kolkata, India.
