Affiliation = {Córdoba, M (Corresponding Author), Univ Nacl Cordoba, Fac Ciencias Agr, Catedra Estadist \& Biometria, Cordoba, Argentina.
   Córdoba, M (Corresponding Author), INTA CONICET, Unidad Fitopatol \& Modelizac Agr UFyMA, Cordoba, Argentina.
   Cordoba, Mariano; Balzarini, Monica, Univ Nacl Cordoba, Fac Ciencias Agr, Catedra Estadist \& Biometria, Cordoba, Argentina.
