   Yu, Shuyan; Deng, Hao; Liu, Zhankun; Chen, Jin; Mao, Xiancheng, Cent South Univ, Hunan Key Lab Nonferrous Resources \& Geol Hazard D, Changsha 410083, Peoples R China.
   Xiao, Keyan, Chinese Acad Geol Sci, Inst Mineral Resources, MNR Lab Metallogeny \& Mineral Resource Assessment, Beijing 100037, Peoples R China.},
