   Wen, Linsheng; Li, Baoyin; Zhou, Yunrui; Weng, Aifang; Cai, Guo; Lin, Yuying, Fujian Normal Univ, Sch Geog Sci, Sch Carbon Neutral Future Technol, Fuzhou 350117, Peoples R China.
