   Bain, Robert E. S., United Nations Childrens Fund UNICEF, Div Data Anal Planning \& Monitoring, 3 United Nations Plaza, New York, NY 10017 USA.
   Yu, Jie, Tongji Univ, Coll Environm Sci \& Engn, Shanghai 200092, Peoples R China.
   Alegana, Victor, Kenya Med Res Inst KEMRI, Populat Hlth Unit, Wellcome Trust Res Programme, Nairobi, Kenya.
   Lin, Yi, Tongji Univ, Coll Surveying \& Geo Informat, Shanghai 200092, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.apgeog.2021.102549},
