   Gu, Tianshun, China Univ Geosci, Sch Environm Studies, Wuhan, Peoples R China.
   Gu, Tianshun; Zhao, Hongbo; Yue, Li; Liu, Yangyang; Guo, Jiaojiao, Henan Univ, Key Res Inst Yellow River Civilizat \& Sustainable, Kaifeng 475001, Peoples R China.
   Gu, Tianshun; Zhao, Hongbo; Yue, Li; Liu, Yangyang; Guo, Jiaojiao, Henan Univ, Collaborat Innovat Ctr Yellow River Civilizat, Henan Prov \& Minist Educ, Kaifeng 475001, Peoples R China.
