   Liu, Maoqi, Hunan Univ Sci \& Technol, Sch Resources Environm \& Safety Engn, Xiangtan 411201, Peoples R China.
   Liu, Maoqi, Hunan Prov Key Lab Coal Resources Clean Utilizat \&, Xiangtan 411201, Peoples R China.
