   Luo, GP (Corresponding Author), Sino Belgian Joint Lab Geoinformat, B-9000 Ghent, Belgium.
   Hellwich, O (Corresponding Author), Tech Univ Berlin, Dept Comp Vis \& Remote Sensing, D-10587 Berlin, Germany.
