   Subedi, Mukti Ram, Univ Georgia, Warnell Sch Forestry \& Nat Resources, Athens, GA 30602 USA.
   McIntyre, Nancy E., Texas Tech Univ, Dept Biol Sci, Lubbock, TX 79409 USA.
   Kahl, Samantha S., Blackburn Coll, Dept Biol, Carlinville, IL 62626 USA.
   Perry, Gad, George Mason Univ, Dept Environm Sci \& Policy, 4400 Univ Dr, Fairfax, VA 22030 USA.
   Song, Xiaopeng, Univ Maryland, Dept Geog Sci, College Pk, MD 20742 USA.},
DOI = {10.3390/rs16152778},
