   Groom, Quentin; Adriaens, Tim; Oldoni, Damiano; Desmet, Peter; Lens, Luc, Res Inst Nat \& Forest INBO, Brussels, Belgium.
   Vanderhoeven, Sonia, Dept Milieu Nat \& Agr, Serv Publ Wallonie, Belgian Biodivers Platform, Gembloux, Belgium.
   De Troch, Rozemien, Royal Meteorol Inst Belgium, Brussels, Belgium.
   Reyserhove, Lien, Meise Bot Garden, Meise, Belgium.
   De Troch, Rozemien, Belgian Climate Ctr, Brussels, Belgium.},
DOI = {10.3389/fevo.2024.1148895},
