Affiliation = {Jiang, ZC; Zhao, LJ (Corresponding Author), MNR \& GZAR Int Res Ctr Karst Ausp UNESCO, Inst Karst Geol, Key Lab Karst Dynam, CAGS, Guilin 541004, Guangxi, Peoples R China.
