   Cheng, Shifen; Zhang, Wenhui; Wang, Lizeng; Lu, Feng, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Geog Sci \& Nat Resources Res, State Key Lab Resources \& Environm Informat Syst, Beijing, Peoples R China.
