   Du, Danying; He, Baozhong; Luo, Xuefeng; Ma, Shilong; Song, Yaning; Yang, Wen, Xinjiang Univ, Xinjiang Key Lab Oasis Ecol, Urumqi 830017, Peoples R China.
   Du, Danying; He, Baozhong; Luo, Xuefeng; Ma, Shilong; Song, Yaning; Yang, Wen, Key Lab Smart City \& Environm Modelling Higher Edu, Urumqi 830017, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.3390/su16072706},
