   Hirmas, Daniel R. R., Texas Tech Univ, Dept Plant \& Soil Sci, Lubbock, TX USA.
   McEwan, Ryan W. W., Univ Dayton, Dept Biol, Dayton, OH USA.
   Mueller, Tom G. G., Heartland Geospatial LLC, Waukee, IA USA.
   Samonil, Pavel, Silva Tarouca Res Inst, Dept Forest Ecol, Brno, Czech Republic.
   Samonil, Pavel, Mendel Univ Brno, Dept Forest Bot Dendrol \& Geobiocoenol, Brno, Czech Republic.},
