   Yang, Jie; Peng, Bin; Guan, Kaiyu, Univ Illinois, Natl Ctr Supercomp Applicat, Urbana, IL 61801 USA.
   Yang, Qi, Max Planck Inst Biogeochem, Dept Biogeochem Integrat, D-07745 Jena, Germany.
   Jia, Xiaowei, Univ Pittsburgh, Dept Comp Sci, Pittsburgh, PA 15260 USA.
