   Erosion; Random forest (RF); soil particle size; spatial distribution;
   two-point machine learning (TPML) model; uncertainty assessment},
Keywords-Plus = {LOESS PLATEAU; GRAIN-SIZE; PREDICTION; SEDIMENTATION; CONSERVATION;
