   Han, Liang; Duan, Jianwen, Shanxi Wanding Space Digital Co Ltd, Shanxi Prov Doctoral Innovat Workstn, Datong 037008, Peoples R China.
   Liang, Baoxing, Shanxi Prov Coal Geol 115 Explorat Inst Co Ltd, Shanxi Tech Innovat Ctr Comprehens Monitoring \& Em, Datong 037003, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.3390/agriculture16050540},
